# 3d Lennard-Jones
label sizeloop

variable mysize index 1 5 10 15 20

units lj
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic

lattice fcc 0.01
region simbox block 0 ${mysize} 0 ${mysize} 0 ${mysize}
create_box 1 simbox
create_atoms 1 box

mass 1 1.0
velocity all create 1.25 87287 dist uniform

pair_style lj/cut 3.0
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0 3.0

fix f all nve

dump 1 all custom 100 dump.task_c_${mysize} id type x y z vx vy vz

thermo 100
thermo_style custom step dt temp xhi
run 50000


clear
next mysize
jump SELF sizeloop
